<!--
    ic_splash_branding.xml — Bottom Branding for Android 12+ Splash

    Shown at the bottom of the splash screen via windowSplashScreenBrandingImage.
    Like Instagram's "from Meta" label.

    Renders: small ferry logo icon on the left + "AquaRoute" rendered as
    a letterform wordmark using geometric path segments.

    Canvas: 400 × 100 viewport (roughly 200×50dp at 2x density)
    Style: semi-transparent white (#CCFFFFFF) to be subtle like Instagram's
-->
